   * You can vote for issues by adding a "thumbs up" (üëç) using the "smile/pick your reaction" menu on the top-right of the issue. See the [prioritized list of open issues](https://github.com/scikit-hep/awkward-1.0/issues?q=is%3Aissue+is%3Aopen+sort%3Areactions-%2B1-desc+reactions%3A%3E0+).
